# amplify
node_modules
.amplify
amplifyconfiguration*
# amplify_outputs.json IS committed on purpose: it holds only public client
# configuration, and without it in the repo the CI build cannot compile.
# `ampx sandbox` / `ampx pipeline-deploy` overwrite it with the real values.
